constituent: rice plant, wheat, cereal, claw, vulture, old days, olden times, stick, sun, day
koohiiStory1: The rice plant is common in Japan because all the wheat was eaten by vultures in the olden times.
koohiiStory2: It used to be that wheat was grown in Japan. However, this was often stolen by vultures, so in olden times, the gods gave the Japanese the rice plant.
